Class StructureSharingList<T>

java.lang.Object
  java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      java.util.AbstractList<T>
          opennlp.ccg.util.StructureSharingList<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>
public class StructureSharingList<T>
extends AbstractList<T>
implements Serializable

An unmodifiable list formed by sequencing two sublists. The sublists are assumed to remain unchanged as well. Equality is checked using == on the list elements, which are assumed to be canonical.
